<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dern-Support - Professional Technical Support Services</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main class="landing-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Professional Technical Support When You Need It Most</h1>
            <p>Dern-Support provides expert technical solutions for all your devices and systems. Fast, reliable, and affordable support for businesses and individuals.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
              <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-accent btn-lg">Get Started</a>
              <a href="#services" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">Explore Services</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3183153/pexels-photo-3183153.jpeg" alt="IT Support Specialist helping a client">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section id="services" class="services section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>Our Expert Services</h2>
          <p>We offer comprehensive technical support solutions to keep your technology running smoothly</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-grid">
          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-desktop fa-2x" style="color: white;"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Computer Repair</h3>
            <p>Expert diagnosis and repair for desktop and laptop computers. Hardware upgrades, virus removal, and system optimization.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-network-wired fa-2x" style="color: white;"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Network Support</h3>
            <p>Setup, troubleshooting, and optimization for home and business networks. Wi-Fi solutions, security implementation, and performance tuning.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt fa-2x" style="color: white;"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Mobile Device Repair</h3>
            <p>Screen replacement, battery service, and data recovery for smartphones and tablets. Fast turnaround and quality parts.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-server fa-2x" style="color: white;"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Business IT Support</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive IT solutions for businesses of all sizes. Managed services, cloud solutions, and strategic technology planning.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="how-it-works section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>How It Works</h2>
          <p>Getting technical support has never been easier</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3>Submit a Request</h3>
            <p>Describe your technical issue and select the urgency level through our easy-to-use portal.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3>Get a Quote</h3>
            <p>Receive an instant cost estimate based on your issue type and urgency requirements.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h3>Schedule Service</h3>
            <p>Choose a convenient time for our certified technician to assist you remotely or on-site.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <h3>Problem Solved</h3>
            <p>Our expert technicians will resolve your issue quickly and efficiently with a satisfaction guarantee.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="knowledge-base-preview">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Extensive Knowledge Base</h2>
        <p>Access our library of technical guides, tutorials, and solutions to common problems. Find answers to your technical questions 24/7.</p>
        <a href="/knowledge/search" class="btn btn-lg">Browse Knowledge Base</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="testimonials section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
          <p>Don't just take our word for it - hear from our satisfied customers</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="testimonial-slider">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <p>"Dern-Support fixed my laptop in less than 24 hours when I had critical work deadlines. Their technician was professional, knowledgeable, and went above and beyond to ensure everything was working perfectly. Excellent service!"</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">- John D., Marketing Director</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="testimonial" style="display: none;">
            <p>"As a small business owner, having Dern-Support handle our IT needs has been a game-changer. They've improved our network performance, implemented better security measures, and provide responsive support whenever we need it."</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">- Sarah M., CEO of Bright Ideas Inc.</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="testimonial" style="display: none;">
            <p>"After struggling with persistent computer issues for months, Dern-Support diagnosed and fixed the problem in one visit. Their pricing was transparent, and the technician explained everything clearly. I highly recommend their services!"</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">- Robert J., Freelance Designer</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
